title: 13 - Gavin Matts
itunes:title: 13 - Gavin Matts
description: Hey, it’s our first episode recorded in the All Things Comedy studio instead of on the road. Can ya tell? Doesn’t matter because we got Gavin Matts, and he’s funny enough to overcome any past audio inconsistencies. You’ve seen this Vancouver boy all over Comedy Central, now take a listen to his tale. Here’s five words to describe this episode: you won’t wanna stop time.
